{
  "stem": "13395.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Wedding bands, anything in jewelry, any silver, candlesticks, any silver that was in the house, under threat of death, had to be delivered to the police.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They meticulously made a list of what you gave them, and you got the piece of paper that you had delivered all that to them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed to wear any fur coats.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they would confiscate even coats with fur collars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is the life that we led at that time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They all-- they all went through the same ordeal that we did.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Upper Silesia became part of Germany proper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It became German Reich again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on October 19, 1939, they came and picked up my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They gave him a few hours warning--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Nazis.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that day I won't forget either. 1939, October 19.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Every year I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was running around when he was ready to go, and had him put on another shirt, another sweater, and one more sweater, because winter is coming, and I don't know where you're going to be and what-- when we will see you again.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At least you'll have clothes, because they weren't allowed to take anything with them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And take another scarf.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all I remember is he turned to me and he said, you take care of mother while I'm gone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had just-- I had just been 14-years-old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a week after my birthday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at 14, now I was no longer a child, because now I had the responsibility to care of my mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--they took all--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took all men, from 16 to 65, from Upper Silesia and shipped them away.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And nobody knew where they went.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
